::Spears::

totally destroyed.  She walked around and saw nothing but destruction 
and debrey from the bomb.  She looked around hoping to find some 
parts that were salvagable. But so far, she found none.  She opene 
dher link, "Striker, the computer room is nothing but melted computer 
parts.  Know of anyplace that me might be able to get comp parts 
from?"
